--- CompleteMazeBuilder TorchPool Reference Fix - 2026-03-04
+++ Assets/Scripts/Core/06_Maze/CompleteMazeBuilder.cs

ISSUE:
======
[SpatialPlacer] TorchPool reference not assigned!

ROOT CAUSE:
===========
SpatialPlacer.PlaceTorches() requires torchPool reference to be assigned,
but CompleteMazeBuilder wasn't wiring up this reference before calling
SpatialPlacer.PlaceAll().

ERROR LOCATION:
===============
Assets/Scripts/Core/08_Environment/SpatialPlacer.cs:537
  if (torchPool == null)
  {
      Debug.LogError("[SpatialPlacer] TorchPool reference not assigned!");
      return;
  }

FIX APPLIED:
============
1. Added code to wire up TorchPool reference to SpatialPlacer
2. Added code to wire up LightPlacementEngine reference to SpatialPlacer
3. Added System.Reflection using statement

CHANGES:
========

